![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/6a8c8e3b-57e0-4f54-be33-f64bb3ec4fd2/processed_20836.jpg)

*   ## **_Jurassic Express def. The Young Bucks in the very same building where the Young Bucks took the AEW Tag Team Championships from them_**
    

WHAT A FKN MATCH?!!

Incredible match that ends with the long lost COUNTDOWN TO EXTINCTION finisher

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/f8ecf443-f74a-47df-8605-49270fbbd9e3/20839.jpg)

Jurassic Express is trying to bury the hatchet with the Young Bucks after this incredible match. They even offered the Bucks some money!

But the Don Callis Family attacks and the Bucks are conflicted but they decided not to get involved.

KENNY OMEGA is here to save Jurassic Express but for a second he asks the Bucks if they're gonna help... Nick says I don't know man.. but Kenny has had enough and he saves Jurassic Express, burying HIS beef with them.

