*   ## **_I QUIT MATCH: Jon Moxley vs Darby Allin_**
    

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/36fa84a7-0b3a-48b6-ad35-dfabeea3aa96/processed_20915.jpg)

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/84935aae-80f3-46fe-8adb-ed417fcd09b1/20933.jpg)

*   ## **_I Quit: Darby Allin def. Jon Moxley_**
    

Tasers, Fish Tanks, Fingernail torture, and Old Man Sting

Every single thing you could imagine happened in this I Quit match.

In the end, after Sting evened the odds, Darby Allin choked Jon Moxley out with the AEW Flag, wrapped it around Moxley's neck, hit a scorpion death drop and then a scorpion death lock to make Jon Moxley quit.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/8b661279-569d-4b98-beb6-0365ddc6702a/20936.jpg)